description: She will brief a powerful UN body via video link on Friday, her team says, as protests continue.
title: Svetlana Tikhanovskaya: Belarus opposition leader to address UN Security Council
title_page: Svetlana Tikhanovskaya: Belarus opposition leader to address UN Security Council - BBC News
maintext: "We said that we need peaceful dialogue and agreement between the regime and society, but we see that the regime is not ready for that. We see that we need to move forward and to show an example to other countries," Lithuanian President Gitanas Nauseda said.
